billboard (1.0.1) harmattan; urgency=low

  * Override other operator logos (and restore on quit).
  * Draw other operator logo onto the billboard, too.
  * Better layout (minimum required size), right-aligned.
  * Elide text that is too wide for the screen.
  * Limit other operator logo size to 120x120px.
  * Option to disable billboard through the UI.
  * Option to show/hide the other operator logo.
  * New settings UI.
  * New text alignment option (left, right center).
  * More robust replacement of sysuid's .css file.

